{"tid":1700153,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"連登仔小勝一仗 共雪比賽避抗議決定取消","createTime":"2019-11-08T10:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T14:26:50.000Z","uid":81680,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a402dbe2701a198e896bddaf0d00c783454a6996","tid":1700153,"uid":81680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:46:02.000Z","msg":"琴日我地組織行動，即晚就有巴打收到通知取消，今日蘋果仲報埋，事實證明對住呢啲仆街公司要以行動來抗議，以後共雪係香港搞親活動大家都記得踴躍參與！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原定在今日（8日）於數碼港舉行的WESG香港電競節2019，大會就在今日宣佈取消，有關比賽的進一步安排會另行通知。疑事件與有連登討論區（LIHKG）網民計劃在今午發起針對遊戲廠商暴雪的行動有關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191108/60245175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191108%2F60245175&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBAexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=09f121b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191108%2F60245175&h=25038885\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191108/60245175</a>"},{"pid":"c6ec2fe18506e32f6422a77cf5c54ef67237a89e","tid":1700153,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"今晚開花"},{"pid":"f3d554f395918becac810fed25111a344216421c","tid":1700153,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QKNTnRr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQKNTnRr.jpg&h=d934b1ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdafbc565ce2fd0337d7d85779200dab76030f88","tid":1700153,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:16:04.000Z","msg":"。。。想重啟十點尻叫 麻煩入嚟睇睇。。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700177</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7acf1ad5f498367f6c4a2